{{zh-hanzi|[[明]][[知]][[山]][[有]][[虎]]，[[偏]][[向]][[虎]][[山]][[行]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: míng zhī shān yŏu hŭ, piàn xiàng hŭ shān xíng
===Etymology===
Literally: clearly know that the mountain has tigers, and yet willfully go toward the mountain with tigers
===Idiom===
# to take a risk despite knowing the dangers involved

